Installing Mongo in single box..


Step1:

wget https://fastdl.mongodb.org/linux/mongodb-linux-x86_64-3.0.6.tgz
tar -zxvf mongodb-linux-x86_64-3.0.6.tgz

Step2:

Create a data directory

mkdir -p /paht/to/mongo/data
chmod -R 777 /paht/to/mongo/data

Step3:
Start services

mongod --dbpath /paht/to/mongo/data &

Step4:

Stop Services

pkill -f mongod




That's It.. :-)


